<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-51-0565 </DOCNO><TEXT>The spatial and energetic properties of an ion cloud confined in an RFquadrupole trap, together with the lifetimes of the confined ions, havebeen computed by statistical methods and recently by a simulation method.The influences of different parameters such as ion mass, buffer gas mass,working point in the stability diagram, 'weak' space-charge and shapeof the velocity distribution of the cooling buffer gas have been investigatedand are described.</TEXT></DOC>